HEADWORD: Putting
<hw>Put"ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The throwing of a
heavy stone, shot, etc., with the hand raised or extended from the
shoulder; -- originally, a Scottish game.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Putting stone</b></col>, <cd>a heavy stone used in the
game of putting.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Putting green</ent>⟦br⟧
